Title: Mycobacterium tuberculosis inhibitor prediction
Description: Identification of active molecules against Mycobacterium tuberculosis using an ensemble of data from ChEMBL25 (Target IDs 360, 2111188 and 2366634). The final model is a stacking model integrating four algorithms, including support vector machine, random forest, extreme gradient boosting and deep neural networks.
Interpretation: Probability of M.tb inhibition (measured as IC50 at cut-off 5 uM)
